summary: Hey guys!  I’m doing some pixel art commissions for fun before school starts up again and I cease to exist. I’ve done these for...
caption:
Hey guys! 

I’m doing some pixel art commissions for fun before school starts up again and I cease to exist. I’ve done these for friends in the past and I found that they always seemed to enjoy them.


TERMS OF SERVICE:

-  I take paypal and will not start the commissions until after you pay. It usually takes me about a day or two to reply to emails, so please be patient.

-  All payments should be in CAD

-  There are no refunds (please)

-  After the sprite is completed, you are allowed ONE set or changes (i.e. a small list that you request ONCE), and no more

-  Please tag/credit me if you re-post! I’d rather you didn’t claim it for yourself so please refrain :(

-  Try to be as clear and concise as you can with your descriptions (reference photos are preferred)

-  Sprites will typically be transparent unless you request a simple or patterned background


10 slots total are available! 9 left now!

To contact me, you can message me on tumblr, or email me at: AloenVeraa@gmail.com

summary: 27 and 40 for Misty in the headcanon meme!
question: 27 and 40 for Misty in the headcanon meme!
answer:
27. What is their biggest regret?

As Misty gets older, I think one of her biggest regrets is taking so long opening up to her sisters. She spends a lot of time acting obstinant and distant and, if she could have held back her temper more as a kid, they probably all would have gotten on better together. (Though another part of her knows that she can’t possibly be the only one to blame because her sisters definitely treated her badly as the youngest sibling of the family.)

40. Would you say that they have a superiority-complex? Inferiority-complex? Neither?

She honestly has some of both of these! When she’s around general company (or her friends), she has no problem bragging about being the cutest or most beautiful girl in the world, she’s absolutely over-confident about it. Buuut her sisters have always been her weakest link. Standing next to them, she always feels she comes up short and has to work harder to be heard or respected. Thankfully, things change a bit when she takes over the gym.

(Toootally forgot this was sitting in my inbox but I remembered to answer it finally! Also, in case I haven’t already been perfectly clear about this in the past, I greatly appreciate Misty’s complicated relationship with her sisters. There’s so much meat to pick apart, you know? :-D)

blog.name: pokegodsandmissingno
blog.title: P̵o̵K̸é̴G̸o̸D̷s̸ and Frightful Things to Come?
blog.description: There is a growing desire and expectation of humans here on Earth in making full contact with PoKéMoN who are still unknown. Back in 1995, when I saw my first UPM (Unindexed Pocket Monster), I found out very quickly that other people thought you were totally crazy if you said you saw such things. The world has changed quite a bit since then when I was a child. In fact, in late 1997, a poll taken in Kanto shows that for the first time ever, more than fifty percent of residents now believe in PokéGODS's. Since then, there have been polls that put the figure at over eighty percent or more.

summary: Banekyu Banette and Mimikyu fusion Ghost/Fairy Type Ability: Disguise/Cursed Body Stats: HP - 70, Atk - 120, Def - 85, SpA - 70,...
caption:
Banekyu

Banette and Mimikyu fusion

Ghost/Fairy Type

Ability: Disguise/Cursed Body

Stats: HP - 70, Atk - 120, Def - 85, SpA - 70, SpD - 105, Spe - 105

The Puppeteer Pokemon

A toy which has been possessed, it’s ghostly arms control to arms on the toy using sticks it has picked up.  It takes good care of itself by stealing buttons from other toys.  The zip on its mouth can be opened, but shouldn’t. 

Request for anon.  I hope you like it. Another Banette fusion.  I’m really enjoying these.
